description:
&lt;p&gt;Northamptonshire Healthcare NHS Foundation Trust is looking for a dynamic and forward thinking Financial Controller.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for all of Financial Services including accounts payable, and receivable departments. A strong track record of delivering financial services will be required along with relevant experience of completing statutory accounts. You will need to be able to provide effective and inspirational leadership to the Directorate alongside close working with colleagues outside of the finance department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for the operational, performance and business management of Financial Services and will contribute to the finance strategy alongside the Financial Management team. The post holder will work under the direction and line management of the Deputy Director of Financial Management &amp; Contracting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CCAB qualified is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJanine JosephJob titleDeputy Director of Financial Management &amp; ContractingEmail addressjanine.joseph@nhft.nhs.ukTelephone number07712 402160&lt;/p&gt;
